## License Verification

To verify the licenses of all dependencies:

```bash
# Check license compatibility
cargo deny check licenses

# List all dependencies with their licenses
cargo deny list
```

## Updating This File

When adding new dependencies, run:

```bash
cargo deny list > /tmp/deps.txt
```

Then update this file with any new licenses.

